d.f: ￹￺to be next to * lean against￻幾乎在一起，靠得很近

e: ￹`Caay~ `ko~ `ta~`tadi'ecen~ `cingra~.￺He is not to be depended upon.￻他是不能依靠的人
￹`Cima~ `ko~ `pi~`tadi'ec~`an~ `iso~ `anini~?￺Whom can you depend on at present?￻你目前依靠誰？現在你能信任誰？
￹`Ma~`tadi'ec~ `no~ `loma'~ `nira~ `ko~ `loma'~ `niyam~.￺His house is next to ours.￻他家緊靠著我們的家
